    <item>
      <title>德意志银行 DWS 恢复公司头衔以安抚员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/deutsche-bank-s-dws-resurrects-corporate-titles-to-mollify-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德意志银行的资产管理部门几年前决定取消企业头衔，导致员工感到不满，现在该部门正在恢复这些头衔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/deutsche-bank-s-dws-resurrects-corporate-titles-to-mollify-staff</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 08:19:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国启动路演，向石油巨头推介大型海上油气资源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/korea-launches-roadshow-to-pitch-big-offshore-find-to-oil-majors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球石油巨头对一处海上油田表现出兴趣之后，韩国目前正在举办投资者路演，这在亚洲国家引发了兴奋和怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/korea-launches-roadshow-to-pitch-big-offshore-find-to-oil-majors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 08:17:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油巨头综述：BP 盈利、Vitol 向交易员支付的款项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/big-oil-roundup-bp-earnings-vitol-s-payout-to-traders-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国能源巨头 BP 公布第二季度强劲收益后，彭博社的 Will Kennedy 和 James Herron 讨论了该公司的业绩。他们还谈到了维多集团去年决定向交易员支付创纪录的 65 亿美元股息，以及更广泛的地缘政治局势对能源市场的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-30/big-oil-roundup-bp-earnings-vitol-s-payout-to-traders-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 08:12:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率决定前欧洲股市因稳健数据走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估该地区最大经济体的增长数据并等待本周晚些时候美国和英国央行的利率决定，欧洲股市小幅走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/european-stocks-hold-steady-on-solid-data-before-rate-decisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 07:22:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司保持回购稳定，利润稳定后提高股息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bp-keeps-buyback-steady-raises-dividend-as-profit-stabilizes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司 (BP Plc) 保持了股票回购步伐，并增加了股息，因为第二季度原油开采带来的强劲盈利抵消了其他业务部门的疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/bp-keeps-buyback-steady-raises-dividend-as-profit-stabilizes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:13:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国批准促进 ESG 投资的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/thai-government-approves-steps-aimed-at-boosting-esg-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国政府批准了旨在提振当地股市的措施，包括增加税收减免和减少个人投资所谓可持续基金的锁定期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/thai-government-approves-steps-aimed-at-boosting-esg-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管德国经济意外下滑，欧元区经济增长仍超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区经济第二季度增长超过预期，主要国家的强劲扩张使该地区摆脱了德国意外经济萎缩的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/france-s-economic-growth-beats-forecasts-in-boost-for-euro-area</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度限制债券持有，阻止全球基金进入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/india-will-shield-some-newly-issued-debt-from-foreign-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度对部分新发行债券的外资持股比例实施了管制，这一出人意料的举措凸显出印度官员对将印度债券纳入全球关键指数后引发的数十亿美元热钱流入感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/india-will-shield-some-newly-issued-debt-from-foreign-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 01:31:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：GDP 数据好坏参半，欧洲股市涨幅缩减</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区主要经济体公布的国内生产总值数据好坏参半，令人对经济复苏步伐产生怀疑，欧洲股市缩减涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 22:47:22 GMT</pubDate>
